{"tid":2156900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"19 歲青年大埔派遊行傳單遇襲　腹部中刀見腸情況嚴重　22 歲內地刀手被捕","createTime":"2020-08-14T18:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T19:10:44.000Z","uid":30944,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b43edb9cdf62fa79b634580694c8f19b72ff7b77","tid":2156900,"uid":30944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"(2019-10-20)今午大埔連儂隧道有 19 歲青年派發 10月20日遊行傳單期間，與一名男子因政見問題爭執，被人用約長 20 厘米的生果刀刺向頸部及腹部，腹部傷口見腸，送院時清醒。傷者友人受訪時稱，刀手曾指「香港係中國嘅」，又斥傷者及朋友「搞亂香港」，最終乘的士逃去。警方其後指，肇事的 22 歲男子涉傷人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n疑兇上的士後自行到大埔警署被捕，是持雙程證的內地人，姓柳。<br />\n<br />\n傷者友人：刀手曾斥「搞亂香港」<br />\n<br />\n傷者友人接受傳媒訪問時稱，他和朋友都不認識行兇者，只是之前派傳單時見過一次，受襲時是第二次遇上該男子。該友人指，行兇男子曾指「香港係中國嘅」，又斥傷者及朋友「搞亂香港」，他又引述在場市民稱，該男子逃跑至富雅花園十字路口上的士離去。<br />\n<br />\n黃兆健則透露，傷者已送到威爾斯親王醫院治理，送院時清醒。<br />\n<br />\n香港警察則在 facebook 專頁稱，下午五時半接獲報案指大埔墟行人隧道內有兩名男子爭執，爭執期間，22 歲男子以一把生果刀襲擊 19 歲男子，傷者已送往威爾斯親王醫院，而 22 歲男子其後被捕。案件現暫列「傷人」，由大埔警區刑事調查隊跟進。警方又強烈譴責暴力行為，指不論任何犯案原因或背景，警方都會嚴肅處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uUF7DF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uUF7DF.jpg&h=3c994e70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/akFYUiO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FakFYUiO.png&h=5326ec67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/大埔連儂隧道街坊派傳單遇襲-腹部中刀重傷見腸-刀手曾斥-搞亂香港/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%96%AE%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%85%B9%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%80%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E8%A6%8B%E8%85%B8-%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%A5-%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcb32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=709fe794\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E9%80%A3%E5%84%82%E9%9A%A7%E9%81%93%E8%A1%97%E5%9D%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%82%B3%E5%96%AE%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%85%B9%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%88%80%E9%87%8D%E5%82%B7%E8%A6%8B%E8%85%B8-%E5%88%80%E6%89%8B%E6%9B%BE%E6%96%A5-%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2F&h=2e2c9bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/大埔連儂隧道街坊派傳單遇襲-腹部中刀重傷見腸-刀手曾斥-搞亂香港/</a><br />\n<br />\n有無人知呢壇野幾時判？"},{"pid":"cb81c5a352ee8c0cbeb5b647772665768858b42d","tid":2156900,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"死支那賤畜"},{"pid":"2994dbd1c2c2c57f7fe75075ff9dd67914481905","tid":2156900,"uid":30944,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"咁快負評，好唔想比人記得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb667122cf45196dff4c872605a6802527af0305","tid":2156900,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:53:23.000Z","msg":"高調拉人"},{"pid":"2c9cb2b8f3fea0491f4d097239ebb1c783e4cec3","tid":2156900,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"FLCC 4677/2019"},{"pid":"9a697a3ed9685eeef56515be98e449603f039779","tid":2156900,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"00bb0e072d081591bd0a18f084aaf00263220a2f","tid":2156900,"uid":125349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:54:17.000Z","msg":"CLS <br />\nbtw 2019年"},{"pid":"904696127bbd9aad434625cab4448b8e6ec0ba83","tid":2156900,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2994dbd1c2c2c57f7fe75075ff9dd67914481905","tid":2156900,"uid":30944,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:52:20.000Z","msg":"咁快負評，好唔想比人記得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"講句舊聞/回帶係咪會中武漢肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52b5201897884d8a217cd988e8d962